'''''Geonosis and the Outer Rim Worlds''''' is a sourcebook for the ''[[Star Wars Roleplaying Game]]'' published by [[Wizards of the Coast]] on [[March 24]], [[2004]].

The book covers historical and major character information related to 26 planets of the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim Territories]] including [[Geonosis/Legends|Geonosis]], [[Kamino/Legends|Kamino]], [[Ryloth/Legends|Ryloth]], and [[Kessel/Legends|Kessel]].

